254
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,841
Sekarang, saya bercakap terus terang,

255
00:13:01,841 --> 00:13:02,801
awak tak dapat biasakan diri pula.

256
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,520
Lecehnya awak.

257
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:08,401
Awak berubah dengan cepat dan mendadak,

258
00:13:08,401 --> 00:13:09,560
saya tak dapat biasakan diri.

259
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,041
Lagipun,

260
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:13,080
