00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,200
Saya sudi.

270
00:13:39,281 --> 00:13:40,200
Saya sangat sudi.

271
00:14:11,161 --> 00:14:11,760
Qi.

272
00:14:12,921 --> 00:14:14,281
Adakah awak rasa lebih gembira
