278
00:14:27,961 --> 00:14:28,880
Awak maksudkan

279
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:30,640
kuda putih saya?

280
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:32,921
Tuan!

281
00:14:32,921 --> 00:14:33,801
Bai Shi dah kembali.

282
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,320
Tenanglah, apa hal?

283
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:36,401
Cik Muda Sang.

284
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:38,281
Komandan Agung...

285
00:14:39,241 --> 00:14:40,721
Komandan Agung ditangkap baginda.

286
00:14:41,921 --> 00:14:42,801
Apa yang terjadi?

287
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,361
Mari kita balik dulu.

288
00:14:46,361 --> 00:14:46,760
Ayuh.

289
00:14:55,740 --> 00:14:56,681
(Telan Awan)

290
00:14:56,721 --> 00:14:57,680
Apa yang terjadi?

291
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:00,440
Saya juga tak tahu.

292
00:15:00,801 --> 00:15:02,721
Semasa saya dan Komandan Agung
bincangkan cara penyelesaian,

293
00:15:02,721 --> 00:15:03,841
tiba-tiba datang beberapa pengawal

294
00:15:03,841 --> 00:15:05,041
